course_title: Seminar in Classical Art and Archaeology - SEM CLS ART&ARCH

sections.comments: Visit https://cnrs.ubc.ca/fall2020courses/ for information on course delivery. Interconnections in the Late Bronze Age Eastern Mediterranean. Cross-listed with NEST 400A, NEST 500D. Majors and Honours seminar for students in Classical, Near Eastern and Religious Studies. Visit cnrs.ubc.ca for full course description.WAITLIST: if this course is full or blocked, or if you do not meet the restrictions, please register in CLST 403B-WL1. Students specializing in CNRS will receive priority registration from the waitlist.

description: Selected topics in Greek or Roman art and archaeology, with an emphasis on research. Restricted to majors and honours students in CLST, CLAS, CLAH, ARGR, GRNE, CNRS.
